data.text: @What46HasDone It’s so nice to hear “continuing to drop”.
@What46HasDone Covid levels are really low.   We are not in a wave anymore, thank God.
@What46HasDone Probably 2 months until BA2 surge comes.
@What46HasDone I'm worried about recent outbreaks in Connecticut and Iowa. Could be a resurgence of Omicron.
@What46HasDone I am still paying attention. It has become increasingly difficult to get data in WA. The State rarely posts data, and not at all at the county level. Counties aren't even bothering.

@What46HasDone I wouldn't say no one.  My wife and I still focus on protecting the kids and ourselves when we go out, and we're fully vaxed.  Numbers are better, but not great yet.

Another surge can surely hit with many not caring still and helping it transmit & mutate more.
